#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/virtualization/_index.adoc:777
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"/usr/local/bin/qemu-system-x86_64  -monitor none \\\n"
"  -cpu qemu64 \\\n"
"  -vga cirrus \\\n"
