#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/virtualization/_index.adoc:1034
msgid ""
"The link:https://www.qemu.org/docs/master/system/monitor.html[QEMU monitor] "
"controls a running QEMU emulator (guest VM)."
msgstr ""
